item.title: Guardiome.org + Guardiome.com
item.description: Guardiome.org makes software to analyze health data. Guardiome.com builds production line to generate health data. We want to help people generate data and plug it into our analytics.
item.content:
Guardiome.org makes software to analyze health data.
